item.title: About
item.description: CINAQ is registered in the Dutch Chamber of Commerce. We specialize in Internet Technologies. In particular the following fields of interest: Software development with Python, Java, Javascript and more DevOps and SRE culture Security, Micro-services and Cloud Native engineering practices Agile Product development Our core belief is “A product is never done”. We strive to make a difference today while looking forward to the future.
